                    I acknowledge and, where necessary, under applicable local law consent to Apple collecting and processing my Personal Information/Data pursuant to Apple’s privacy policies and in accordance with the rights of workers enshrined in such applicable laws. I am aware that Apple will process this information in order to improve and maintain effective personnel administration, for general business management purposes, and to comply with obligations imposed by law including right to work and export control requirements. I have been provided a copy of Apple’s Employee Privacy Policy.
                </p>
